raw.data <- fread("Speed Dating Data.csv", encoding = "UTF-8")

gender01

gender <- unique(raw.data[, c(1, 3)])  # iidiidgender
gender <- ddply(gender, .(gender), summarize, cnt = length(gender))  # gender
gender$gender <- c("", "")  # gender0,1,
gender$gender <- factor(gender$gender, levels = c("",""))
p1 <- ggplot(gender, aes(x = gender, y = cnt, fill = gender)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.7) +
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  geom_text(aes(label = cnt), vjust = -0.2) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "", values = c("darkorange", "dodgerblue4")) +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = c("", ""))
p1

race1-6

race <- unique(raw.data[, c(1, 3, 40)])  # iidiidgenderrace
race <- ddply(race, .(race, gender), summarize, cnt = length(race))  # race 
race <- na.omit(race)  # NA
race$gender <- factor(race$gender, levels = c(0, 1), labels = c("", ""))  # gender0,1,
race$race <- factor(race$race, levels = 1:6, labels = c("", "", "", "", "", ""))  # race1~6
p2 <- ggplot(race, aes(x = race, y = cnt, fill = gender)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") +
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  geom_text(aes(label = cnt), vjust = -0.2, position = position_dodge(0.9)) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "", values = c("darkorange", "dodgerblue4")) +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = c("", "", "", "", ""))
p2

wave6wave9sportsyoga17ggplot

hobby <- raw.data[raw.data$wave > 6 & raw.data$wave < 9, ]  # wave6wave9
hobby <- unique(hobby[, c(1, 51:67)])  # iidiid
hobby <- na.omit(hobby)  # NA
names <- colnames(hobby[, 2:18])  # colname
means <- as.vector(colMeans(hobby[, 2:18]))  # colmean
average <- data.frame(hobby = names, mean = means)  # dataframe
average$hobby = factor(average$hobby, levels = c("gaming", "museums", "music", "hiking", "theater", "yoga", "movies", "tvsports", "tv", "art", "shopping", "sports", "dining", "clubbing", "exercise", "reading", "concerts"), labels = c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", ""))  # averagehobby
p3 <- ggplot(average, aes(x = hobby, y = mean)) +
  geom_bar(fill = "darkred", stat = "identity") +
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = c("", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust = 1))
p3

\(A_2\) \[ H(D|A_2=)=-\frac{5}{5}\log\frac{5}{5}=0 \\ H(D|A_2=)=-\frac{4}{10}\log\frac{4}{10}-\frac{6}{10}\log\frac{6}{10}=0.971\\ H(D|A_2)=\frac{10}{15}\times 0.971=0.647\\ g(D,A_2)=0.971-0.647=0.324 \] \(A_3\) \[ H(D|A_3=)=-\frac{6}{6}\log\frac{6}{6}=0 \\ H(D|A_3=)=-\frac{3}{9}\log\frac{3}{9}-\frac{6}{9}\log\frac{6}{9}=0.918\\ H(D|A_3)=\frac{9}{15}\times 0.918=0.551\\ g(D,A_3)=0.971-0.551=0.420 \] \(A_4\) \[ H(D|A_4=)=-\frac{1}{5}\log\frac{1}{5}-\frac{4}{5}\log\frac{4}{5}=0.722 \\ H(D|A_4=)=-\frac{4}{6}\log\frac{4}{6}-\frac{2}{6}\log\frac{2}{6}=0.918\\ H(D|A_4=)=-\frac{4}{4}\log\frac{4}{4}=0\\ H(D|A_4)=\frac{5}{15}\times 0.722+\frac{6}{15}\times 0.918=0.608\\ g(D,A_4)=0.971-0.608=0.363 \] \[ g(D,A_2)=0.324\\ g(D,A_3)=0.420\\ g(D,A_4)=0.363 \]
